lyrics:
[Verse]
In dimly lit halls, we face our fears
As animatronic monsters draw near
Their haunting eyes, a menacing glow
Surviving the night, we won't let go

[Chorus]
Five Nights at Freddy's, the terror unfolds
In this haunted world, where nightmares behold
We're trapped in this nightmare, fighting back the fright
Locked in this rock song, we'll make it through the night
